text.section:
The Video Lottery Facility Location Commission established under § 9-1A-36 of this subtitle may not:
award more than six video lottery operation licenses;
award more than 16,500 video lottery terminals for operation at video lottery facilities in the State;
subject to the requirements of § 9-1A-36(h) and (i) of this subtitle, award more than 4,750 terminals for operation at any video lottery facility; and
for a location in Allegany County:
award a video lottery operation license to an applicant that does not agree to purchase the Rocky Gap Lodge and Resort; and
notwithstanding § 9-1A-36(i)(2) of this subtitle, award more than 1,500 video lottery terminals for operation at a video lottery facility in Allegany County.
